ItemCard:Blade Dance

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search
Blade Dance (Base)
Spell Information
School
Pip Cost3
Accuracy100%
Type
Spell Description
Applies a +45% Random Damage Blade and an additional +45% Random Damage Blade for all allies
Blade Dance Spell Animation
